<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 00:35:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际法院以色列新法官抨击种族灭绝听证会“在思想上不诚实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</link><description>佩雷斯学术中心院长罗恩·夏皮拉教授被吹捧为现任政府可能任命的最高法院法官，政府希望任命一名保守派法官</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</guid></item><item><title>青少年被以色列国防军招募从事情报行动，然后因间谍活动被判入狱，起诉国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/teen-recruited-by-idf-for-intelligence-operation-then-jailed-for-espionage-sues-state/00000190-6fd6-d705-a7f5-ffffc0890000</link><description>双桅船。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的新任军事部长罗曼·戈夫曼将军批准在一场“影响力运动”中使用这名 16 岁男孩。在针对国家提起的诉讼中，该青少年声称他在拘留期间受到虐待</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:27:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/teen-recruited-by-idf-for-intelligence-operation-then-jailed-for-espionage-sues-state/00000190-6fd6-d705-a7f5-ffffc0890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布，以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸军事行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-during-west-bank-military-operation/00000190-6e6b-d6fc-afba-ef7bfd000000</link><description>在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡尔姆附近的努尔沙姆斯难民营的夜间行动中，一辆军车下爆炸装置引爆，造成一名以色列士兵死亡，另一名以色列士兵重伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:37:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-during-west-bank-military-operation/00000190-6e6b-d6fc-afba-ef7bfd000000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和勒庞的教训：以色列中左翼合并如何阻止极右翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-01/ty-article/.highlight/lessons-from-netanyahu-and-le-pen-how-israels-center-left-merger-can-halt-the-far-right/00000190-6f56-d0bf-a9fd-6ffe924c0000</link><description>以色列工党与左翼梅雷茨的合并，是左翼和中间派如何抵制独裁民族主义浪潮的起点和蓝图</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-01/ty-article/.highlight/lessons-from-netanyahu-and-le-pen-how-israels-center-left-merger-can-halt-the-far-right/00000190-6f56-d0bf-a9fd-6ffe924c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-6f36-dbfd-a5d1-efb717810000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，中士。来自贝尔谢巴的 21 岁男子奥里·伊茨查克·哈达 (Ori Itzchak Hadad) 在爆炸中丧生。另有一名士兵在事件中受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:18:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-6f36-dbfd-a5d1-efb717810000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡总理私人住宅附近的耶路撒冷市中心街道大门施工开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/construction-on-gate-blocking-jerusalem-street-near-pm-netanyahus-private-home-begins/00000190-6f2c-d9e6-af9d-6ffefb5a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷私人住宅旁边的永久大门可用于封锁整条街道，近几个月来，该地区一直是反政府抗议活动的场所，抗议活动要求释放在加沙被扣押的人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/construction-on-gate-blocking-jerusalem-street-near-pm-netanyahus-private-home-begins/00000190-6f2c-d9e6-af9d-6ffefb5a0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列士兵在加沙使用被拘留者作为“人体盾牌”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/report-israeli-soldiers-filmed-using-detainees-in-gaza-as-human-shields/00000190-6f2b-d6fc-afba-ef7b8ad20000</link><description>半岛电视台发布的视频片段显示，士兵命令身穿以色列军装、身上安装有随身摄像机的巴勒斯坦人在士兵之前进入建筑物和隧道开口</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/report-israeli-soldiers-filmed-using-detainees-in-gaza-as-human-shields/00000190-6f2b-d6fc-afba-ef7b8ad20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 269 天：西班牙要求加入国际法院针对以色列的请愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-269-spain-asks-to-join-icj-petition-against-israel/00000190-6f40-d9e6-af9d-6fd2e7830001</link><description>以色列释放了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院院长以及其他约 50 名巴勒斯坦人 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特表示，他们并不了解这一决定 ■ 西班牙要求加入南非请愿书，在国际法院指控以色列犯下种族灭绝罪 ■ 斯莫特里奇称他批准了五个新的定居点，作为对单方面承认巴勒斯坦国的国家的回应 ■ 这是战争开始 269 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-269-spain-asks-to-join-icj-petition-against-israel/00000190-6f40-d9e6-af9d-6fd2e7830001</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女背着X走来走去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-in-israel-walking-around-with-an-x-on-their-back/00000190-5f34-d747-add0-dffddac50000</link><description>记者罗尼·辛格最近的电视报道透露，有一个新单位的存在，旨在帮助拯救遭到暗杀的以色列妇女。她解释了为什么现在唯一的解决方案是给他们在海外新的生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-in-israel-walking-around-with-an-x-on-their-back/00000190-5f34-d747-add0-dffddac50000</guid></item><item><title>加沙渔民声称自己的船只在战争中被毁，以色列拒绝退还押金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-denies-deposit-refund-to-gaza-fishermen-who-say-their-boats-were-destroyed-in-war/00000190-6e8e-d4b8-a7b9-fe8f2cb70000</link><description>战前因超出捕鱼界限而被扣押的两名渔民交了 4 万美元押金才取回船只。法院表示，他们必须提供船只受损情况的照片，但这是不可能的，因为他们逃到了加沙南部，无法返回北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-denies-deposit-refund-to-gaza-fishermen-who-say-their-boats-were-destroyed-in-war/00000190-6e8e-d4b8-a7b9-fe8f2cb70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在加沙海岸外的浮动援助运送码头是否总是沉在水中？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</link><description>这个耗资 2.3 亿美元的浮动码头在加沙海岸附近的两个月内仅运营了 28 天。更糟糕的是，6500吨物资中的大部分仍在等待国际机构领取，而不是到达巴勒斯坦人手中</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙地面上与以色列“幽灵部队”进行战斗，几乎不被人看到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</link><description>多域部队的以色列士兵在加沙行动中使用机器人、无人机和机密仪器。当我们陪同他们在加沙市中心执行任务时，有一件事明显缺席</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>在特拉维夫举行的重大和平活动之前，以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在美国各地集会要求停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</link><description>周日，包括以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在内的数百名抗议者在北美各地城市举行抗议活动，呼吁结束战争、返回人质并支持特拉维夫的“现在是时候”和平集会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管担心反犹太主义，但在加沙战争紧张局势中，LGBTQ 犹太人在纽约骄傲游行中找到了团结</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/despite-antisemitism-fears-lgbtq-jews-find-solidarity-at-nyc-pride-march-amid-gaza-war/00000190-6d95-d9ec-a19e-ef95228e0000</link><description>周日，数千名参与者和数百万观众挤满了纽约街头，其中包括挥舞着大卫之星骄傲旗帜、以色列人质的黄丝带和“自由巴勒斯坦”花车的 LGBTQ 犹太人。一位活动人士表示，“各个年龄段的酷儿犹太人都大胆而热情地参加了骄傲游行”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/despite-antisemitism-fears-lgbtq-jews-find-solidarity-at-nyc-pride-march-amid-gaza-war/00000190-6d95-d9ec-a19e-ef95228e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民事务部长奇克利表示，勒庞担任法国总统“对以色列非常有利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/diaspora-affairs-minister-chikli-says-le-pen-as-french-president-excellent-for-israel/00000190-6d11-d9ec-a19e-ef150a860000</link><description>这位极右翼的全国集会领袖因其政党历史性的反犹太主义而受到法国犹太团体无条件的反对。然而，以色列侨民事务部长对她的立场“印象深刻”，并补充说内塔尼亚胡似乎“持同样的观点”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/diaspora-affairs-minister-chikli-says-le-pen-as-french-president-excellent-for-israel/00000190-6d11-d9ec-a19e-ef150a860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列释放加沙希法医院院长；部长们猛烈抨击国防，辛贝特酋长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-director-ministers-slam-defense-shin-bet-chiefs/00000190-6d20-d499-a5bf-edbe84ad0000</link><description>这一决定激起了以色列部长们的愤怒，一些人要求撤换辛贝特的负责人。以色列监狱管理局和辛贝特发表了相互矛盾的声明来解释释放事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-director-ministers-slam-defense-shin-bet-chiefs/00000190-6d20-d499-a5bf-edbe84ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府成员加剧了黎巴嫩爆发全面冲突的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/despite-risks-big-war-in-north-beckons-govt/00000190-6aad-d01f-abbe-7fad4b790000</link><description>对政府无法允许约 60,000 名以色列人返回黎巴嫩边境附近家园的批评越来越多。政府可能会试图寻求摆脱与真主党僵局的出路，并冒着全面战争的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 03:36:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/despite-risks-big-war-in-north-beckons-govt/00000190-6aad-d01f-abbe-7fad4b790000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称以色列即将“消灭哈马斯军队”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-live/idf-18-soldiers-wounded-one-seriously-in-earlier-drone-explosion-in-northern-israel/00000190-6c13-db88-abb0-6e3729f00005</link><description>以色列国防军呼吁巴勒斯坦人撤离汗尤尼斯东部社区 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，政府并不知道释放 Al-Shifa 医院院长的决定 ■ 梅图拉的房屋遭到火箭袭击 ■ 西班牙要求加入国际法院对以色列的种族灭绝指控 ■ Gallant称以色列军队立即需要1万名士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 03:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-live/idf-18-soldiers-wounded-one-seriously-in-earlier-drone-explosion-in-northern-israel/00000190-6c13-db88-abb0-6e3729f00005</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长们支持赋予议会权力挑选司法监察员的法案；总检察长反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</link><description>该法案将让候选人由立法者以无记名投票的方式批准，而不是由司法任命委员会批准。法院管理顾问批评该法案，称其是“旨在削弱司法部门权力的政权更迭运动的一部分”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准更改农业部名称 可能耗资高达200万谢克尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</link><description>在阿维·迪希特部长要求改变后，该部现更名为农业和粮食安全部。以色列优质政府运动猛烈抨击了“投资数百万谢克尔进行无用的表面改变”的“妄想和不必要”的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>